Restaurant Logo-PNG\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-69bjclgl fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>M\u1eeaNG NG&Agrave;Y QU\u1ed0C KH&Aacute;NH PH&Aacute;P T\u1ea0I NH&Agrave; H&Agrave;NG REFLECTIONS<\/strong><\/h3>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 365px;top: -11.125px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-68h42uts fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">GI\u1ea2M GI&Aacute; 25% CHO T\u1ea4T C\u1ea2 C&Aacute;C KH&Aacute;CH&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1eafm ch&igrave;m v&agrave;o cu\u1ed9c phi&ecirc;u l\u01b0u \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c s\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph&aacute;p khi ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m Ng&agrave;y Qu\u1ed1c Kh&aacute;nh Ph&aacute;p ngay gi\u1eefa l&ograve;ng S&agrave;i G&ograve;n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H&eacute; l\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t c&aacute;c m&oacute;n \u0103n c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n \u0111&iacute;ch th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Ph&aacute;p, m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u h&agrave;nh tr&igrave;nh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi m&oacute;n Escargot truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi B\u01a1 th\u1ea3o m\u1ed9c t\u1ecfi, ti\u1ebfp theo l&agrave; S&uacute;p h&agrave;nh t&acirc;y ki\u1ec3u Ph&aacute;p v\u1edbi b&aacute;nh m&igrave; ph&ocirc; mai th\u01a1m ngon. Sau \u0111&oacute;, h&atilde;y th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c m&oacute;n th\u0103n b&ograve; m\u1ecdng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung h&agrave;i h&ograve;a b\u1edfi v\u1ecb b&eacute;o ng\u1eady c\u1ee7a gan ng\u1ed7ng.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">K\u1ebft th&uacute;c bu\u1ed5i d\u1ea1 ti\u1ec7c \u0103n u\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi m&oacute;n b&aacute;nh ng\u1ecdt Mille Feuille Vanilla tinh t\u1ebf, n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb tinh t\u1ebf v&agrave; v&ocirc; s\u1ed1 l\u1edbp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ng\u1eafm nh&igrave;n khung c\u1ea3nh th&agrave;nh ph\u1ed1 ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c t\u1eeb khung c\u1ea3nh trang nh&atilde; c\u1ee7a Nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng Reflections.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* Th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n 5 m&oacute;n ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb \u200b\u200b1.590.000++ VN\u0110\/ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* N&acirc;ng cao tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang ch\u1ec9 1.390.000++ VN\u0110 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">* \u01afu \u0111&atilde;i &aacute;p d\u1ee5ng t\u1eeb ng&agrave;y 14\/7 \u0111\u1ebfn ng&agrave;y 21\/7, t\u1eeb 17h30 &ndash; 22h00<\/p>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute;left: 448px;top: 284.453px\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\">&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-69bjht9p ffg-empty-space fg-text-dark\"><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-513fi7l5 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><section class=\"ffb-id-5db87sav fg-section fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--2 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5gsvhb fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5h0eq1 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5h0kd5 buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Reflections-French-5-course-scaled.jpg\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\"><span class=\"btn-text\">XEM MENU<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5h0cnh fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-3 fg-text-dark\"><div class=\"ffb-id-6c5h0j0t buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tablecheck.com\/vi\/shops\/reflections-restaurant\/reserve\" class=\"ffb-block-button-2-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-md    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-butto